snippet: Democrats held on to an open Congressional seat as returns in a special election showed that Suzanne Bonamici would complete the term of former Representative David Wu.
abstract: Democrats keep open Congressional seat in Oregon as returns in special election show that Democrat Suzanne Bonamici is well ahead of Republican rival Rob Cornilles, and will complete the term of former Rep David Wu.
lead_paragraph: Democrats held on to an open Congressional seat as returns in a special election showed that Suzanne Bonamici would complete the term of former Representative David Wu.

headline.seo: Bonamici, Oregon Democrat, to Complete David Wu’s Term
